{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":673,"text":"Vision is the most important"},{"time":3055,"text":"and prioritized sense that we have."},{"time":5643,"text":"We are constantly looking"},{"time":7327,"text":"at the world around us,"},{"time":9101,"text":"and quickly we identify and make sense"},{"time":11298,"text":"of what it is that we see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13633,"text":"Let's just start with an example"},{"time":15552,"text":"of that very fact."},{"time":16825,"text":"I'm going to show you\na photograph of a person,"},{"time":18835,"text":"just for a second or two,"},{"time":20638,"text":"and I'd like for you to identify"},{"time":22533,"text":"what emotion is on his face."},{"time":24672,"text":"Ready?"},{"time":25900,"text":"Here you go. Go with your gut reaction."},{"time":28612,"text":"Okay. What did you see?"},{"time":30943,"text":"Well, we actually surveyed"},{"time":33207,"text":"over 120 individuals,"},{"time":35514,"text":"and the results were mixed."},{"time":37464,"text":"People did not agree"},{"time":39731,"text":"on what emotion they saw on his face."},{"time":42621,"text":"Maybe you saw discomfort."},{"time":44426,"text":"That was the most frequent response"},{"time":46415,"text":"that we received."},{"time":47670,"text":"But if you asked the person on your left,"},{"time":49759,"text":"they might have said regret or skepticism,"},{"time":52500,"text":"and if you asked somebody on your right,"},{"time":54429,"text":"they might have said\nsomething entirely different,"},{"time":57323,"text":"like hope or empathy."},{"time":60143,"text":"So we are all looking"},{"time":61702,"text":"at the very same face again."},{"time":64804,"text":"We might see something"},{"time":66232,"text":"entirely different,"},{"time":68615,"text":"because perception is subjective."},{"time":71679,"text":"What we think we see"},{"time":73847,"text":"is actually filtered"},{"time":75289,"text":"through our own mind's eye."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77693,"text":"Of course, there are many other examples"},{"time":79946,"text":"of how we see the world\nthrough own mind's eye."},{"time":82361,"text":"I'm going to give you just a few."},{"time":84143,"text":"So dieters, for instance,"},{"time":86803,"text":"see apples as larger"},{"time":88821,"text":"than people who are not counting calories."},{"time":91841,"text":"Softball players see the ball as smaller"},{"time":95474,"text":"if they've just come out of a slump,"},{"time":97629,"text":"compared to people who \nhad a hot night at the plate."},{"time":101173,"text":"And actually, our political beliefs also"},{"time":104123,"text":"can affect the way we see other people,"},{"time":106365,"text":"including politicians."},{"time":108538,"text":"So my research team and I\ndecided to test this question."},{"time":112231,"text":"In 2008, Barack Obama\nwas running for president"},{"time":115862,"text":"for the very first time,"},{"time":117261,"text":"and we surveyed hundreds of Americans"},{"time":120243,"text":"one month before the election."},{"time":122466,"text":"What we found in this survey"},{"time":124165,"text":"was that some people, some Americans,"},{"time":126451,"text":"think photographs like these"},{"time":128147,"text":"best reflect how Obama really looks."},{"time":131139,"text":"Of these people, 75 percent"},{"time":133761,"text":"voted for Obama in the actual election."},{"time":136628,"text":"Other people, though,\nthought photographs like these"},{"time":139796,"text":"best reflect how Obama really looks."},{"time":142085,"text":"89 percent of these people"},{"time":144061,"text":"voted for McCain."},{"time":145882,"text":"We presented many photographs of Obama"},{"time":149388,"text":"one at a time,"},{"time":150985,"text":"so people did not realize\nthat what we were changing"},{"time":153884,"text":"from one photograph to the next"},{"time":155737,"text":"was whether we had artificially lightened"},{"time":157793,"text":"or darkened his skin tone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160341,"text":"So how is that possible?"},{"time":161901,"text":"How could it be that\nwhen I look at a person,"},{"time":164736,"text":"an object, or an event,"},{"time":166457,"text":"I see something very different"},{"time":168432,"text":"than somebody else does?"},{"time":170261,"text":"Well, the reasons are many,"},{"time":172551,"text":"but one reason requires that we understand"},{"time":174802,"text":"a little bit more about how our eyes work."},{"time":177355,"text":"So vision scientists know"},{"time":179364,"text":"that the amount of information"},{"time":180847,"text":"that we can see"},{"time":182718,"text":"at any given point in time,"},{"time":184557,"text":"what we can focus on,\nis actually relatively small."},{"time":187254,"text":"What we can see with great sharpness"},{"time":189983,"text":"and clarity and accuracy"},{"time":192160,"text":"is the equivalent"},{"time":194147,"text":"of the surface area of our thumb"},{"time":196323,"text":"on our outstretched arm."},{"time":198618,"text":"Everything else around that is blurry,"},{"time":200757,"text":"rendering much of what is presented"},{"time":203198,"text":"to our eyes as ambiguous."},{"time":205842,"text":"But we have to clarify"},{"time":208116,"text":"and make sense of what it is that we see,"},{"time":210364,"text":"and it's our mind that\nhelps us fill in that gap."},{"time":213749,"text":"As a result, perception\nis a subjective experience,"},{"time":217318,"text":"and that's how we end up seeing"},{"time":218777,"text":"through our own mind's eye."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221005,"text":"So, I'm a social psychologist,"},{"time":222818,"text":"and it's questions like these"},{"time":224335,"text":"that really intrigue me."},{"time":226048,"text":"I am fascinated by those times"},{"time":227699,"text":"when people do not see eye to eye."},{"time":230196,"text":"Why is it that somebody might"},{"time":231893,"text":"literally see the glass as half full,"},{"time":234505,"text":"and somebody literally sees it"},{"time":235985,"text":"as half empty?"},{"time":237456,"text":"What is it about what one person\nis thinking and feeling"},{"time":240577,"text":"that leads them to see the world"},{"time":242124,"text":"in an entirely different way?"},{"time":244484,"text":"And does that even matter?"},{"time":246947,"text":"So to begin to tackle these questions,"},{"time":249998,"text":"my research team and I\ndecided to delve deeply"},{"time":252637,"text":"into an issue that has received"},{"time":254487,"text":"international attention:"},{"time":256405,"text":"our health and fitness."},{"time":258128,"text":"Across the world,"},{"time":259486,"text":"people are struggling\nto manage their weight,"},{"time":261888,"text":"and there is a variety of strategies"},{"time":264102,"text":"that we have to help us\nkeep the pounds off."},{"time":267459,"text":"For instance, we set\nthe best of intentions"},{"time":270565,"text":"to exercise after the holidays,"},{"time":273262,"text":"but actually, the majority of Americans"},{"time":275860,"text":"find that their New Year's resolutions"},{"time":277902,"text":"are broken by Valentine's Day."},{"time":280958,"text":"We talk to ourselves"},{"time":282460,"text":"in very encouraging ways,"},{"time":284154,"text":"telling ourselves this is our year"},{"time":285987,"text":"to get back into shape,"},{"time":287688,"text":"but that is not enough to bring us back"},{"time":289530,"text":"to our ideal weight."},{"time":291265,"text":"So why?"},{"time":293101,"text":"Of course, there is no simple answer,"},{"time":295184,"text":"but one reason, I argue,"},{"time":297947,"text":"is that our mind's eye"},{"time":299873,"text":"might work against us."},{"time":301474,"text":"Some people may literally see exercise"},{"time":304493,"text":"as more difficult,"},{"time":306159,"text":"and some people might literally"},{"time":307973,"text":"see exercise as easier."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310280,"text":"So, as a first step\nto testing these questions,"},{"time":314028,"text":"we gathered objective measurements"},{"time":316291,"text":"of individuals' physical fitness."},{"time":319137,"text":"We measured the \ncircumference of their waist,"},{"time":321479,"text":"compared to the \ncircumference of their hips."},{"time":324735,"text":"A higher waist-to-hip ratio"},{"time":326204,"text":"is an indicator of being\nless physically fit"},{"time":328387,"text":"than a lower waist-to-hip ratio."},{"time":330459,"text":"After gathering these measurements,"},{"time":332686,"text":"we told our participants that"},{"time":334499,"text":"they would walk to a finish line"},{"time":336083,"text":"while carrying extra weight"},{"time":337966,"text":"in a sort of race."},{"time":339123,"text":"But before they did that,"},{"time":340910,"text":"we asked them to estimate the distance"},{"time":343350,"text":"to the finish line."},{"time":345037,"text":"We thought that the physical\nstates of their body"},{"time":347333,"text":"might change how\nthey perceived the distance."},{"time":350818,"text":"So what did we find?"},{"time":352578,"text":"Well, waist-to-hip ratio"},{"time":355286,"text":"predicted perceptions of distance."},{"time":358302,"text":"People who were out of shape and unfit"},{"time":360932,"text":"actually saw the distance\nto the finish line"},{"time":363030,"text":"as significantly greater"},{"time":364193,"text":"than people who were in better shape."},{"time":366084,"text":"People's states of their own body"},{"time":368125,"text":"changed how they\nperceived the environment."},{"time":371361,"text":"But so too can our mind."},{"time":373477,"text":"In fact, our bodies and our minds"},{"time":375386,"text":"work in tandem"},{"time":377363,"text":"to change how we see the world around us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":379971,"text":"That led us to think that maybe people"},{"time":382066,"text":"with strong motivations"},{"time":383344,"text":"and strong goals to exercise"},{"time":385164,"text":"might actually see\nthe finish line as closer"},{"time":388336,"text":"than people who have weaker motivations."},{"time":392036,"text":"So to test whether motivations"},{"time":394378,"text":"affect our perceptual\nexperiences in this way,"},{"time":397730,"text":"we conducted a second study."},{"time":399653,"text":"Again, we gathered objective measurements"},{"time":402334,"text":"of people's physical fitness,"},{"time":404338,"text":"measuring the circumference of their waist"},{"time":406396,"text":"and the circumference of their hips,"},{"time":408164,"text":"and we had them do a \nfew other tests of fitness."},{"time":411529,"text":"Based on feedback that we gave them,"},{"time":414072,"text":"some of our participants told us"},{"time":415637,"text":"they're not motivated\nto exercise any more."},{"time":417945,"text":"They felt like they already\nmet their fitness goals"},{"time":420339,"text":"and they weren't going\nto do anything else."},{"time":422472,"text":"These people were not motivated."},{"time":424091,"text":"Other people, though, \nbased on our feedback,"},{"time":426233,"text":"told us they were highly \nmotivated to exercise."},{"time":428518,"text":"They had a strong goal\nto make it to the finish line."},{"time":431230,"text":"But again, before we had them\nwalk to the finish line,"},{"time":434227,"text":"we had them estimate the distance."},{"time":436197,"text":"How far away was the finish line?"},{"time":437945,"text":"And again, like the previous study,"},{"time":440307,"text":"we found that waist-to-hip ratio"},{"time":442141,"text":"predicted perceptions of distance."},{"time":444101,"text":"Unfit individuals saw\nthe distance as farther,"},{"time":448733,"text":"saw the finish line as farther away,"},{"time":450703,"text":"than people who were in better shape."},{"time":452650,"text":"Importantly, though, this only happened"},{"time":454659,"text":"for people who were not motivated"},{"time":456593,"text":"to exercise."},{"time":458212,"text":"On the other hand,"},{"time":459802,"text":"people who were highly\nmotivated to exercise"},{"time":462846,"text":"saw the distance as short."},{"time":465043,"text":"Even the most out of shape individuals"},{"time":467370,"text":"saw the finish line"},{"time":468928,"text":"as just as close,"},{"time":470432,"text":"if not slightly closer,"},{"time":472267,"text":"than people who were in better shape."}]},{"cues":[{"time":474923,"text":"So our bodies can change"},{"time":476882,"text":"how far away that finish line looks,"},{"time":479120,"text":"but people who had committed\nto a manageable goal"},{"time":483039,"text":"that they could accomplish\nin the near future"},{"time":485148,"text":"and who believed that they were capable"},{"time":487342,"text":"of meeting that goal"},{"time":488938,"text":"actually saw the exercise as easier."},{"time":492354,"text":"That led us to wonder,"},{"time":494264,"text":"is there a strategy that we could use"},{"time":496681,"text":"and teach people that would help"},{"time":499071,"text":"change their perceptions of the distance,"},{"time":501340,"text":"help them make exercise look easier?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":503821,"text":"So we turned to\nthe vision science literature"},{"time":506455,"text":"to figure out what should we do,"},{"time":508201,"text":"and based on what we read,\nwe came up with a strategy"},{"time":510683,"text":"that we called, \"Keep \nyour eyes on the prize.\""},{"time":514061,"text":"So this is not the slogan"},{"time":515872,"text":"from an inspirational poster."},{"time":517757,"text":"It's an actual directive"},{"time":520005,"text":"for how to look around your environment."},{"time":522927,"text":"People that we trained in this strategy,"},{"time":525219,"text":"we told them to focus\ntheir attention on the finish line,"},{"time":529093,"text":"to avoid looking around,"},{"time":530929,"text":"to imagine a spotlight"},{"time":532270,"text":"was shining on that goal,"},{"time":533893,"text":"and that everything around it was blurry"},{"time":536372,"text":"and perhaps difficult to see."},{"time":538178,"text":"We thought that this strategy"},{"time":540349,"text":"would help make the exercise look easier."},{"time":542842,"text":"We compared this group"},{"time":544461,"text":"to a baseline group."},{"time":546119,"text":"To this group we said,"},{"time":547324,"text":"just look around the environment"},{"time":548911,"text":"as you naturally would."},{"time":550160,"text":"You will notice the finish line,"},{"time":551720,"text":"but you might also notice"},{"time":553423,"text":"the garbage can off to the right,"},{"time":555292,"text":"or the people and the \nlamp post off to the left."},{"time":557578,"text":"We thought that people\nwho used this strategy"},{"time":560263,"text":"would see the distance as farther."}]},{"cues":[{"time":562365,"text":"So what did we find?"},{"time":564812,"text":"When we had them estimate the distance,"},{"time":566785,"text":"was this strategy successful"},{"time":568533,"text":"for changing their perceptual experience?"},{"time":571033,"text":"Yes."},{"time":572231,"text":"People who kept their eyes on the prize"},{"time":574436,"text":"saw the finish line as 30 percent closer"},{"time":577485,"text":"than people who looked around"},{"time":579096,"text":"as they naturally would."},{"time":580376,"text":"We thought this was great."},{"time":581684,"text":"We were really excited because it meant"},{"time":583566,"text":"that this strategy helped make"},{"time":585046,"text":"the exercise look easier,"},{"time":586938,"text":"but the big question was,"},{"time":588872,"text":"could this help make exercise"},{"time":590709,"text":"actually better?"},{"time":592100,"text":"Could it improve the quality"},{"time":593765,"text":"of exercise as well?\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":595646,"text":"So next, we told our participants,"},{"time":597909,"text":"you are going to walk to the finish line"},{"time":599804,"text":"while wearing extra weight."},{"time":602031,"text":"We added weights to their ankles"},{"time":604051,"text":"that amounted to 15 percent\nof their body weight."},{"time":606748,"text":"We told them to lift their knees up high"},{"time":608696,"text":"and walk to the finish line quickly."},{"time":610915,"text":"We designed this exercise in particular"},{"time":613075,"text":"to be moderately challenging"},{"time":614797,"text":"but not impossible,"},{"time":616574,"text":"like most exercises"},{"time":617834,"text":"that actually improve our fitness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":620676,"text":"So the big question, then:"},{"time":623336,"text":"Did keeping your eyes on the prize"},{"time":625448,"text":"and narrowly focusing on the finish line"},{"time":627780,"text":"change their experience of the exercise?"},{"time":630545,"text":"It did."},{"time":632140,"text":"People who kept their eyes on the prize"},{"time":634375,"text":"told us afterward that it required"},{"time":636189,"text":"17 percent less exertion"},{"time":638284,"text":"for them to do this exercise"},{"time":639954,"text":"than people who looked around naturally."},{"time":643393,"text":"It changed their subjective experience"},{"time":645457,"text":"of the exercise."},{"time":647080,"text":"It also changed the objective nature"},{"time":650092,"text":"of their exercise."},{"time":651391,"text":"People who kept their eyes on the prize"},{"time":653639,"text":"actually moved 23 percent faster"},{"time":656287,"text":"than people who looked around naturally."},{"time":659735,"text":"To put that in perspective,"},{"time":661417,"text":"a 23 percent increase"},{"time":663090,"text":"is like trading in your\n1980 Chevy Citation"},{"time":666975,"text":"for a 1980 Chevrolet Corvette."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671619,"text":"We were so excited by this,"},{"time":674131,"text":"because this meant that a strategy"},{"time":676298,"text":"that costs nothing,"},{"time":677980,"text":"that is easy for people to use,"},{"time":679747,"text":"regardless of whether they're in shape"},{"time":681718,"text":"or struggling to get there,"},{"time":683576,"text":"had a big effect."},{"time":685016,"text":"Keeping your eyes on the prize"},{"time":686573,"text":"made the exercise look and feel easier"},{"time":689517,"text":"even when people were working harder"},{"time":692075,"text":"because they were moving faster."},{"time":694294,"text":"Now, I know there's more to good health"},{"time":697264,"text":"than walking a little bit faster,"},{"time":699286,"text":"but keeping your eyes on the prize"},{"time":701471,"text":"might be one additional strategy"},{"time":703101,"text":"that you can use to help promote"},{"time":704710,"text":"a healthy lifestyle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":707025,"text":"If you're not convinced yet"},{"time":709106,"text":"that we all see the world\nthrough our own mind's eye,"},{"time":711626,"text":"let me leave you with one final example."},{"time":713653,"text":"Here's a photograph of a beautiful \nstreet in Stockholm, with two cars."},{"time":717076,"text":"The car in the back looks much larger"},{"time":719267,"text":"than the car in the front."},{"time":720693,"text":"However, in reality,"},{"time":722299,"text":"these cars are the same size,"},{"time":724678,"text":"but that's not how we see it."},{"time":727573,"text":"So does this mean that"},{"time":729697,"text":"our eyes have gone haywire"},{"time":731411,"text":"and that our brains are a mess?"},{"time":733981,"text":"No, it doesn't mean that at all."},{"time":736553,"text":"It's just how our eyes work."},{"time":738574,"text":"We might see the world in a different way,"},{"time":741263,"text":"and sometimes that might not"},{"time":743035,"text":"line up with reality,"},{"time":745101,"text":"but it doesn't mean\nthat one of us is right"},{"time":747226,"text":"and one of us is wrong."},{"time":749321,"text":"We all see the world\nthrough our mind's eye,"},{"time":751457,"text":"but we can teach ourselves\nto see it differently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":754308,"text":"So I can think of days"},{"time":756132,"text":"that have gone horribly wrong for me."},{"time":758166,"text":"I'm fed up, I'm grumpy, I'm tired,"},{"time":760562,"text":"and I'm so behind,"},{"time":762102,"text":"and there's a big black cloud"},{"time":764508,"text":"hanging over my head,"},{"time":765991,"text":"and on days like these,"},{"time":767425,"text":"it looks like everyone around me"},{"time":769300,"text":"is down in the dumps too."},{"time":771434,"text":"My colleague at work looks annoyed"},{"time":773167,"text":"when I ask for an extension on a deadline,"},{"time":775877,"text":"and my friend looks frustrated"},{"time":777855,"text":"when I show up late for lunch\nbecause a meeting ran long,"},{"time":780554,"text":"and at the end of the day,"},{"time":782147,"text":"my husband looks disappointed"},{"time":784173,"text":"because I'd rather go to \nbed than go to the movies."},{"time":786706,"text":"And on days like these,\nwhen everybody looks"},{"time":789723,"text":"upset and angry to me,"},{"time":791731,"text":"I try to remind myself that there\nare other ways of seeing them."},{"time":794949,"text":"Perhaps my colleague was confused,"},{"time":798259,"text":"perhaps my friend was concerned,"},{"time":800695,"text":"and perhaps my husband was \nfeeling empathy instead."},{"time":803962,"text":"So we all see the world"},{"time":805856,"text":"through our own mind's eye,"},{"time":807682,"text":"and on some days, it might look"},{"time":809685,"text":"like the world is a dangerous"},{"time":811093,"text":"and challenging and insurmountable place,"},{"time":813630,"text":"but it doesn't have to look\nthat way all the time."},{"time":816600,"text":"We can teach ourselves\nto see it differently,"},{"time":818796,"text":"and when we find a way to make the world"},{"time":821462,"text":"look nicer and easier,"},{"time":823399,"text":"it might actually become so."}]},{"cues":[{"time":825739,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":827294,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}